@softwbc, I reproduce the problem and find the reason of the problem.

the sharding column `docId` is `String` type, but the sharding configuration is `{docId % 10}`. `String` type could not do `% operation` so the route failed.

you can use `t_doc_process_$->{docId.hashCode() % 10}` replace `test.t_doc_process_$->{docId % 10}` and retry, the problem can be solved.

